## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent biases in the sources used. Some sources may have regional biases or may not account for recent technological advancements in reducing emissions from gasoline cars. Additionally, the report does not cover the potential benefits of gasoline cars, such as their role in economic development and personal mobility.

